#: ../../source/reference/dataframe/generated/maxframe.dataframe.Series.notna.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.dataframe.Series.notna"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.missing.checkna.notna:1 of
msgid "Detect existing (non-missing) values."
msgstr "检测存在的（非缺失）值。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.missing.checkna.notna:3 of
msgid ""
"Return a boolean same-sized object indicating if the values are not NA. "
"Non-missing values get mapped to True. Characters such as empty strings "
"``''`` or :attr:`numpy.inf` are not considered NA values (unless you set "
"``pandas.options.mode.use_inf_as_na = True``). NA values, such as None or"
" :attr:`numpy.NaN`, get mapped to False values."
msgstr ""
"返回一个与原对象大小相同的布尔值对象，表示值是否不是 NA。非缺失值会被映射"
"为 True。诸如空字符串 ``''`` 或 :attr:`numpy.inf` 这样的字符不被认为是 NA"
" 值（除非你设置了 ``pandas.options.mode.use_inf_as_na = True``）。NA 值，"
"例如 None 或 :attr:`numpy.NaN`，会被映射为 False。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.missing.checkna.notna of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.missing.checkna.notna:10 of
msgid ""
"Mask of bool values for each element in DataFrame that indicates whether "
"an element is not an NA value."
msgstr "一个布尔值掩码，用于 DataFrame 中的每个元素，表示该元素是否不是 NA 值。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.missing.checkna.notna of
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

